thread.title: Sharon G
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Sharon G

author: Sharon G
title: Sharon G
text: David was very proactive but not pushy, he was able to expose our property to a lot of potential buyers who would potentially satisfy our price range. The campaign went well and we were given feedback along the way which was great. In particular being remote in another state we felt well informed right throughout and that our sale was in good hands. To top it all off we had a great result which we were thrilled about! Couldn't be happier to have worked with David and his team!
